nodes.text: Dutonian was a Human male mercenary working on Alderaan during the Cold War. In 3643 BBY Skavak hired him and his men to lay an ambush for the Voidhound in the Hangar RS-32 of Pallista Spaceport on Alderaan. The mercenary's confidence in the numbers against the smuggler led to his death in the firefight.

Sergeant Dutonian led a group of mercenaries that did freelance work for the various Alderaanian Houses during the Alderaan Civil War. In the year 3643 BBY, Dutonian accepted a contract from the notorious criminal Skavak to ambush a smuggler in Hangar RS-32 on Alderaan.
